et%20up%20automatic%20deposits%20to%20these%20accounts%20each%20month.%20It's%20not%20a%20lot%20%E2%80%94%20somewhere%20between%20%2435%20and%20%2450%20each%20month%20for%20each%20kid%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20builds%20up%20better%20and%20faster%20than%20you%20think%20it%20will.%20My%2010-year-old's%20account%20has%20earned%20more%20interest%20than%20I've%20contributed%20at%20this%20point.%20They%20all%20have%20more%20money%20to%20go%20to%20college%20than%20I%20did%2C%20even%20the%202-year-old.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5ef29eb-1eb0-478c-9a79-27ea4eceeeff%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBudgeting%20practice%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHave%20you%20ever%20told%20a%20kid%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20%2425%20to%20spend%20on%20your%20birthday%20gift%20%E2%80%94%20can%20you%20find%20something%20under%20that%20amount%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20will%20figure%20it%20out.%20They're%20up%20for%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20stick%20to%20my%20guns%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20offer%20to%20make%20up%20the%20%245%20difference%20for%20a%20%2430%20toy%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20cool.%20It%20doesn't%20sound%20like%20a%20big%20deal%20to%20just%20chip%20in%20%245%2C%20but%20a%20little%20disciplined%20spending%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223996554-5cbd-46cc-9749-93737baac7d4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20buy%20things%20second-hand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKids%20learn%20more%20by%20seeing%20what%20you%20do%20than%20by%20what%20you%20say.%20We%20keep%20our%20own%20spending%20habits%20(and%20attitudes)%20in%20check.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20often%20buy%20household%20goods%20secondhand.%20You%20can%20save%20at%20least%2090%25%20off%20the%20sticker%20price%2C%20and%20there's%20always%20someone%20you%20know%20giving%20away%20baby%20gear%20or%20kid%20clothes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%20stu