%20can%20also%20select%20filters%20or%20categories%20such%20as%20images%2C%20videos%2C%20news%2C%20and%20shopping%20to%20narrow%20my%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20Search%20worked%20better%20when%20I%20had%20a%20specific%20prompt%20or%20question%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20I%20have%20an%20open-ended%20research%20query%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20President%20Gerald%20Ford's%20most%20notable%20accomplishment%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BHow%20did%20Gerald%20Ford's%20legacy%20differ%20from%20other%20presidents%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20would%20probably%20turn%20to%20ChatGPT%20Search%20because%20it%20can%20organize%20information%20concisely%2C%20and%20save%20me%20from%20reading%20hundreds%20of%20related%20articles%20that%20might%20not%20address%20that%20specific%20question%20or%20contain%20those%20keywords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20lead%20in%20offering%20keyword-based%20access%20to%20the%20wider%20web%20is%20tough%20to%20beat.%20While%20I%20see%20valuable%20uses%20for%20both%20products%2C%20I%20don't%20see%20how%20ChatGPT%20Search%20could%20replace%20for%20me%20what%20Google%20has%20spent%20decades%20building%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-search-default-web-browser-engine-compared-google-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735639381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677328076b318443a944e7a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-search-default-web-browser-engine-compared-google-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ChatGPT%20Search%20helps%20users%20find%20quick%20answers%20based%20on%20up-to-date%20information%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20kept%20returning%20to%20Google.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww