20part%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20number%20of%20people%20tacking%20%26quot%3BReddit%26quot%3B%20onto%20their%20search%20terms%20%E2%80%94%20a%20demand%20the%20company%20will%20try%20to%20meet%20with%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-answers-how-it-works-performs-early-access-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReddit%20Answers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20new%20AI-powered%20search%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20out%20what%20this%20year%20has%20looked%20like%20on%20the%20inside%2C%20BI%20asked%2011%20Reddit%20executives%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%26quot%3BSnoos%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Reddit%20calls%20its%202%2C000%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20to%20share%20their%20favorite%20highlights%20behind%20the%20scenes%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bfront%20page%20of%20the%20internet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20described%20some%20career-defining%20moments%20and%20talked%20about%20managing%20through%20rapid%20change%20and%20a%20new%20level%20of%20pressure.%20Here's%20what%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reddit%20execs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676d9873a3e82c7912046f59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThree%20of%2011%20Reddit%20execs%20BI%20spoke%20to%20(from%20left%20to%20right)%3A%20Roxy%20Young%2C%20Laura%20Nestler%2C%20and%20Serkan%20Piantino.%3Cp%3EReddit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6d95de9-3776-4dd5-ae44-9beabf0a53cd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20meant%20to%20take%20Reddit%20public%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20pretend%20that%20this%20all%20makes%20sense%2C%20and%20it's%20all%20business%20as%20usual%20for%20a%20little%20bit.%20But%20there%20are%20moments%20where%20I%20kind%20of%20zone%20out%20and%20realize%20the%20scale%20and%20how%20cool%20a%20moment%20I'm%20in.%20I%20guess%20the%20word%20to%20describe%20it%20is%20'awe.'%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3ESerkan%20Piantino%2C%2041%2C%20VP%20of%20product%2C%20New%20York%20City.%20Joined%20Reddit%20in%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20always%20going%20to%20be%20individuals%20that%20say%2C%20'Reddit%20is%20not%20what%20it%20used%20to%20be.'%20Of%20course%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20what%20it%20used%20to%20be.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20what%20we%20make%20it%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EDavid%20Trencher%2C%2043%2C%20senior%20managing%20director%2C%20large%20customer%20sales%2C%20EMEA%20%26amp%3B%20Australia%2C%20London.%20Joined%20the%20company%20in%202019.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B2024%20has%20been%20maybe%20the%20highlight%20of%20my%20career%20at%20Reddit.%20We%20are%20so%20focused%20on%20starting%20with%20community.%20I%20think%20in%20'24%20we've%20embraced%20that%20value%20more%20than%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Laura%20Nestler%2C%20VP%20of%20community%2C%20Seattle.%20Joined%20Reddit%20in%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225eaf9125-c2e0-409d-8f94-b774acefb582%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIPO%20day%20was%20'so%20Reddit%2C'%20execs%20said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reddit%20Listing%20Day%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676d96997236dcf54aa262de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223241%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReddit%20employees%20gather%20at%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20for%20listing%20day.%3Cp%3ENYSE%3A%20RDDT%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20Snoo%20(the%20company's%20mascot)%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%20(rather%20than%20our%20CEO)%20was%20just%20so%20Reddit-y.%20It%20was%20a%20culmination%20of%20so%20many%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20to%20get%20here%2C%20and%20to%20see%20it%20all%20come%20to%20fruition%20in%20a%20very%20Reddit%20way%20was%20awesome.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%3Cem%3E%20Paulita%20David%2C%20Senior%20Managing%20Director%2C%20large%20customer%20sales%20in%20North%20America.%20Joined%20Reddit%20in%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20broadcast%20live%20globally%2C%20and%20I%20got%20to%20emcee%20the%20entire%20thing%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%20We%20all%20got%20to%20see%20and%20feel%20what%20was%20happening.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EMichelle%20Lozzi%2C%2040%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20experience%2C%20San%20Francisco.%20Joined%20Reddit%20in%202017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20nice%20having%20our%20new%20Snoo%20mascot%20up%20there%20ringing%20the%20bell%2C%20symbolizing%20our%20employees%20and%20the%20community.%20There%20is%20a%20human%20in%20there.%20We%20cannot%20reveal%20who%20it%20is%2C%20but%20the%20only%20clue%20I%20can%20share%20is%20you%20have%20to%20be%205'10%26quot%3B%20to%20wear%20the%20suit.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EMonica%20Benson%2C%2038%2C%20head%20of%20brand%20operations%20and%20creative%20production%2C%20Los%20Angeles.%20Joined%20Reddit%20in%202020.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289566fd1-d898-4b73-b6e4-3ee71a0c42ab%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20execs%20managed%20through%20change%20and%20volatility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20change%20for%20us%20has%20been%20just%20the%20sheer%20volume%20of%20advertisers%20wanting%20to%20advertise%20on%20Reddit.%20It%20impacts%20my%20job%20pretty%20dramatically.%20With%20this%20increased%20demand%2C%20we're%20really%20embracing%20more%20automation.%26quot%3B%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20David%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20run%20a%20lot%20of%20experiments%2C%20so%20failure%20is%20a%20day-to-day%20thing.%20Many%20of%20our%20experiments%20just%20don't%20pan%20out%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20job%20is%20to%20refine%20the%20idea%20and%20keep%20going%20or%20decide%20to%20work%20on%20something%20else.%20We're%20not%20a%20huge%20company.%20We%20still%20have%20limited%20resources%2C%20so%20we%20have%20to%20prioritize.%26quot%3B%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20Piantino%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20balance%20of%20excitement%20and%20pressure%20that%20keeps%20me%20grounded.%20The%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20a%20real%20share%20price%20that%20we%20can%20use%20to%20measure%20our%20size%20adds%20somewhat%20to%20the%20pressure%2C%20but%20ultimately%20the%20excitement%20and%20enthusiasm%20outweigh%20it.%20Something%20we%20try%20to%20instill%20in%20our%20culture%20is%20to%20not%20get%20too%20high%20with%20the%20highs%2C%20and%20too%20low%20with%20the%20lows.%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Jesse%20Rose%2C%2038%2C%20head%20of%20investor%20relations%2C%20Massachusetts%2C%20Joined%20Reddit%20in%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20what%20volatility%20looks%20like%2C%20and%20I%20know%20how%20much%20that%20can%20be%20a%20distraction%20for%20the%20team.%20I%20liked%20being%20a%20calming%20force%20and%20reminding%20people%20that%2C%20some%20days%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20say%20great%20things%20about%20you.%20Some%20days%20they're%20going%20to%20say%20bad%20things%20about%20you%2C%20but%20you%20are%20never%20as%20good%20or%20as%20bad%20as%20they%20say%20you%20are.%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Piantino%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20(two-year%20pre-IPO%20period)%20helped%20us%20prepare%20our%20teams%2C%20which%20helped%20alleviate%20some%20stress.%20We%20were%20going%20into%20it%20knowing%20what%20we%20needed%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3ETrencher%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20our%20communities%20are%20growing%20really%20fast%2C%20and%20that%20can%20be%20a%20challenge.%20There%20are%20a%20bunch%20of%20tools%20that%20moderators%20can%20now%20use%20to%20handle%20moments%20of%20accelerated%20growth.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3ENicole%20Heard%2C%2036%2C%20UK%20country%20lead%2C%20London.%20Joined%20Reddit%20in%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad2e7314-ad