0message%20to%20other%20actors%20in%20the%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHinton%20won%20the%202024%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%20physics%20in%20October.%20He's%20known%20as%20the%20godfather%20of%20AI%20for%20his%20work%20in%20neural%20networks%20and%20he%20%3Cspan%3Espent%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20at%20Google%20before%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeoffrey-hinton-godfather-of-ai-quits-google-sounds-alarm-chatbots-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Equitting%20in%20May%202023%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20was%20launched%20as%20a%20nonprofit%20research%20organization%20in%202015.%20Hinton's%20comments%20come%20as%20OpenAI%20takes%20steps%20towards%20becoming%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-one-step-closer-becoming-profit-company-report-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor-profit%20company%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20who%20co-founded%20OpenAI%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-chatgpt-openai-ceo-career-net-worth-ycombinator-prepper-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Fblog%2Fopenai-supporters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20its%20board%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202018%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20trying%20to%20block%20that%20move.%20Last%20month%2C%20his%20lawyers%20filed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25421711-musk-vs-altman-petition-for-injunction-against-openais-transition-to-for-profit-entity%2F%3Fresponsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einjunction%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20OpenAI%20to%20stop%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-one-step-closer-becoming-profit-company-report-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_bl