cans%20tells%20the%20oft-repeated%20but%20doomed-to-be-ignored%20story%20of%20the%20triumph%20of%20self-interest%20over%20every%20lofty-sounding%20principle.%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy%20represent%20a%20social%20class%20that%20sees%20politics%20as%20a%20necessary%20means%20to%20the%20end.%20It%20is%20the%20same%20principle%20at%20work%20when%20Trump%20threatens%20India%20with%20trade%20tariffs%20despite%20proclaiming%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20love%20Hindoo%E2%80%9D.%20Indian-origin%20supporters%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%2C%20the%20smart%20ones%20at%20least%2C%20bank%20on%20this%20principle%3A%20the%20self-interest%20of%20tech%20and%20finance%20moguls%20may%20reign%20in%20the%20racist%20tendencies%20of%20those%20who%20see%20immigrants%20as%20a%20threat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20utilitarian%20principle%20in%20assessing%20who%20is%20worthy%20of%20being%20an%20American%20is%20on%20full%20display%20here.%20Tech%20bigwigs%20cannot%20continue%20to%20carry%20on%20their%20businesses%20without%20highly%20skilled%20foreign%20workers.%20Small%20businesses%20or%20agriculture%20entrepreneurs%20rely%20on%20unskilled%20foreign%20labourers%2C%20ideally%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%20so%20that%20they%20can%20be%20hired%20for%20less%20than%20minimum%20wages.%20Asylum-seekers%20suit%20nobody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nativists%20in%20Trump's%20broader%20support%20base%20are%20feeling%20let%20down%20by%20his%20big%20tech%20allies%20and%20vice%20versa.%20But%20what%20were%20these%20tech%20moguls%20thinking%3F%20That%20they%20would%20not%20be%20resented%20for%20their%20wealth%20and%20clout%20after%20designing%20and%20funding%20a%20political%20campaign%20that%20kept%20hammering%20on%20how%20average%20Americans%20have%20been%20defrauded%20of%20their%20rightful%20dues%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98outsiders'%20and%20their%20domestic%20cheerleaders%2C%20i.e.%20Democrats%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDouble%20Jeopardy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20working%20class%2C%20including%20immigrant%20groups%20such%20as%20Hispanics%2C%20Asians%2C%20and%20South%20Asians%2C%20rallied%20behind%20the%20Republicans%20because%20they%20felt%20left%20out%20by%20the%20broken%20%E2%80%98system'%20that%20Trump%20promised%20to%20fix%20in%20their%20favour.%20His%20announced%20cabinet%20of%20millionaires%20is%20the%20first%20jolt%20to%20that%20promise.%20Many%20may%20be%20wondering%20how%20their%20concerns%20around%20the%20prices%20of%20eggs%20and%20bacon%20can%20even%20be%20understood%20by%20those%20who%20never%20think%20twice%20before%20buying%20islands%20and%20social%20media%20platforms.%20And%20when%20the%20same%20billionaires%20seem%20to%20be%20threatening%20their%20prospects%20of%20getting%20jobs%2C%20it's%20a%20double%20jeopardy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndians%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20Seattle%20may%20be%20forgiven%20for%20being%20baffled%20at%20the%20moment.%20Are%20they%20insiders%20or%20outsiders%3F%20What%20will%20it%20take%20for%20them%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20people%20who%20are%20building%20this%20country%20and%20not%20%E2%80%9Cthird-world%20invaders%E2%80%9D%20despite%20their%20green%20cards%20or%20even%20American%20passports%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20anyone%20surprised%20that%20Ramaswamy%20is%20facing%20racial%20slurs%20from%20his%20fellow%20MAGA%20supporters%3F%20The%20adage%20%E2%80%9Cnobody%20is%20free%20until%20everyone%20is%E2%80%9D%20needs%20to%20be%20paid%20more%20heed%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20this%20mayhem.%20Exclusionary%20political%20campaigns%20have%20a%20terrible%20habit%20of%20altering%20their%20course%20to%20make%20the%20shooter%20the%20target.%20Prejudice%20boomerangs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Jermaine%2C%20a%20Jamaican%20Uber%20driver%20living%20in%20Florida%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20(Republicans)%20have%20everything%20now%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20White%20House%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%A6who%20are%20they%20going%20to%20blame%20for%20their%20failures%3F%20Us%20Jamaicans%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20Jermaine%2C%20they'll%20blame%20each%20other.%20Happy%20New%20Year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3ENishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735632720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fpsv0rg3_vivek-ramaswamy-afp_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-vs-maga-when-prejudice-boomerangs-7369240%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Why%20is%20anyone%20surprised%20that%20Ramaswamy%20is%20facing%20racial%20slurs%20from%20his%20fellow%20MAGA%20supporters%3F%20The%20adage%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20is%20free%20until%20everyone%20is%26quot%3B%20needs%20to%20be%20paid%20more%20heed%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20this%20mayhem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-vs-maga-when-prejudice-boomerangs-7369240%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kartik%20expands%20his%20real%20estate%20portfolio%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735632111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116823785%2Cimgsize-24154.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkartik-aaryan-expands-his-real-estate-portfolio-in-mumbai-amid-rumors-of-rs-50-crore-fee-for-karan-johars-film%2Farticleshow%2F116823830.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116823830.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBollywood%20actor%20Kartik%20Aaryan%20continues%20to%20rise%20in%20his%20career%20and%20real%20estate%20investments.%20While%20charging%20Rs%2050%20