cularism%20%26amp%3B%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20(%40pinarayivijayan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpinarayivijayan%2Fstatus%2F1873979370869797249%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Narayan%20Rane%2C%2042-year-old%20Nitesh%20Rane%20handles%20the%20portfolios%20of%20fisheries%20and%20ports%20development%20in%20the%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20government.%20Targeting%20Congress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20at%20a%20public%20gathering%2C%20Mr%20Rane%20said%20the%20siblings%20were%20elected%20from%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20because%20the%20state%20is%20%26quot%3Bmini%20Pakistan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKerala%20is%20mini%20Pakistan%20that%20is%20why%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20sister%20are%20elected%20from%20there.%20All%20terrorists%20vote%20for%20them.%20This%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20you%20can%20ask.%20They%20have%20become%20MPs%20after%20taking%20terrorists%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20drew%20a%20scathing%20response%20from%20the%20Opposition%20parties.%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Atul%20Londhe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20else%20can%20one%20expect%20from%20Nitesh%20Rane%3F%20He%20has%20been%20elected%20to%20do%20this%20only.%20However%2C%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%20The%20person%20(Rane)%20is%20a%20minister%20and%20has%20taken%20the%20oath%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20(maintain)%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20unity%20of%20India.%20Now%2C%20he%20is%20labelling%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20states%20as%20Pakistan.%20He%20is%20calling%20the%20voters%20there%20'terrorists.'%20Should%20he%20have%20the%20right%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20ministerial%20position%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Anand%20Dubey%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%20are%20worried%20since%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20won%20only%20by%20a%20lakh%20votes%2C%20they%20are%20not%20able%20to%20digest%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20win%20(by%20a%20margin%20of%204%20lakh%20votes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClyde%20Crasto%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Sharad-Pawar-led%20NCP%20(SP)%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNitesh%20Rane%20always%20speaks%20like%20this%2C%20BJP%20will%20have%20to%20clear%20whether%20they%20agree%20with%20these%20statements.%20The%20BJP%20will%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Kerala%20and%20India.%20These%20statements%20can%20only%20come%20from%20people%20who%20are%20out%20of%20mind.%20It%20is%20like%20an%20insult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20growing%20controversy%2C%20Mr%20Rane%20issued%20a%20clarification.%20%26quot%3BKerala%20is%20very%20much%20part%20of%20India.%20However%2C%20the%20decreasing%20population%20of%20Hindus%20is%20something%20everyone%20should%20worry%20about.%20The%20religious%20conversion%20of%20Hindus%20into%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20has%20become%20an%20everyday%20thing%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735631280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-04%2F16eucm18_pinarayi-vijayan_625x300_03_April_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpinarayi-vijayan-responds-to-bjp-leader-nitesh-ranes-kerala-mini-pakistan-remark-7369277%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20has%20slammed%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Nitesh%20Rane's%20%26quot%3Bmini%20Pakistan%26quot%3B%20remark%20on%20the%20southern%20state.%20He%20has%20described%20the%20remark%20as%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20malicious%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Butterly%20condemnable%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpinarayi-vijayan-responds-to-bjp-leader-nitesh-ranes-kerala-min