he%20police%20smelled%20a%20rat.%20Samples%20from%20the%20body%20in%20the%20car%20were%20sent%20for%20forensic%20tests%20and%20the%20results%20did%20not%20match%20the%20samples%20collected%20from%20the%20family's%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20police%20dug%20deeper%2C%20they%20found%20Parmar%20had%20taken%20huge%20loans%20to%20build%20a%20hotel%20and%20was%20neck-deep%20in%20debt.%20Looking%20for%20a%20way%20out%2C%20he%20planned%20to%20fake%20his%20death%20in%20a%20car%20accident%20so%20that%20his%20family%20could%20get%20an%20accident%20cover%20worth%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20an%20insurance%20payout%20of%20Rs%2023%20lakh.%20The%20plan%20was%20that%20Parmar%20would%20go%20into%20hiding%20till%20his%20family%20received%20the%20money%2C%20the%20investigation%20revealed.%20The%20hotelier%20roped%20in%20some%20relatives%2C%20including%20his%20brother%2C%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20challenge%20was%20arranging%20the%20body%20that%20could%20be%20passed%20off%20as%20his.%20Parmar%20and%20the%20others%20decided%20to%20steal%20a%20body%20from%20the%20nearby%20cremation%20ground.%20It%20must%20be%20pointed%20out%20here%20that%20some%20Hindu%20sects%20in%20Gujarat%20bury%20their%20dead%20instead%20of%20cremating%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20accused%2C%20including%20Parmar%2C%20entered%20the%20cremation%20ground%20late%20at%20night%20and%20dug%20out%20a%20body%20buried%20four%20months%20back.%20This%20body%20was%20then%20put%20into%20Parmar's%20car%20and%20the%20vehicle%20was%20set%20on%20fire%20to%20stage%20the%20accident%20and%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20established%20that%20the%20body%20in%20the%20car%20did%20not%20belong%20to%20Parmar%2C%20police%20faced%20the%20big%20question%3A%20whose%20body%20was%20it%3F%20When%20they%20scanned%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20village%20cremation%20ground%2C%20they%20found%20four%20men%20moving%20a%20body%20at%20night.%20When%20the%20accused%20seen%20in%20the%20video%20were%20grilled%2C%20they%20admitted%20to%20putting%20the%20dug-out%20corpse%20into%20Parmar's%20car%20and%20setting%20it%20on%20fire.%20The%20stolen%20body%20was%20later%20identified%20as%20that%20of%20Ramesh%20Solanki%2C%20who%20died%20four%20months%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanaskantha%20police%20superintendent%20Akshayraj%20Makwana%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20police%20have%20found%20that%20Parmar%20and%20the%20other%20accused%20stole%20the%20body%2C%20put%20it%20into%20the%20car%20and%20set%20the%20vehicle%20on%20fire%20to%20claim%20insurance%20money%20in%20the%20hotelier's%20name.%20%26quot%3BFour%20accused%20were%20part%20of%20the%20conspiracy.%20Three%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20main%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInputs%20by%20Mahendra%20Prasad%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735628880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F8epjgte_gujarat-hotelier_625x300_31_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-body-in-burnt-car-leads-cops-to-hoteliers-grisly-plan-to-clear-debts-7368919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20debt-ridden%20hotelier%20in%20Gujarat's%20Banaskantha%20district%20faked%20his%20death%20in%20a%20car%20accident%20to%20claim%20life%20insurance%20worth%20Rs%201.26%20crore.%20The%20meticulous%20plan%2C%20however%2C%20was%20foiled%20by%20the%20police.%20Dalpat%20Singh%20Parmar%20is%20on%20the%20run%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-body-in-burnt-car-leads-cops-to-hoteliers-grisly-plan-to-clear-debts-7368919%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arjun%20Kapoor%20on%20Career%20Reinvention%20Through%20Villainous%20Turn%20in%20%E2%80%98Singham%20Again%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98I%20Wanted%20to%20be%20Consumed%20at%20a%20Big%20Level%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735628821000%2