3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20BJP%20holds%20power%20in%2020%20states%20and%20has%20been%20in%20control%20of%20Gujarat%20for%2030%20years%20and%20asked%20why%20the%20party%20had%20not%20shown%20respect%20for%20priests%20and%20granthis%20in%20those%20states%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20emphasised%20that%20his%20government%20had%20set%20an%20example%20by%20implementing%20the%20scheme%20in%20Delhi%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20BJP%20should%20replicate%20the%20initiative%20in%20its%20states%20instead%20of%20criticising%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20people%20have%20been%20abusing%20me%20since%20yesterday%2C%20ever%20since%20the%20Pujari%20Granthi%20Samman%20Yojana%20was%20announced.%20My%20question%20to%20them%20is%2C%20will%20the%20country%20benefit%20from%20abusing%20me%3F%20You%20have%20governments%20in%2020%20states.%20You%20have%20been%20in%20power%20in%20Gujarat%20for%2030%20years.%20Why%20haven't%20you%20respected%20the%20priests%20and%20granthis%20there%20till%20now%3F%20Come%20on%2C%20do%20it%20now%3F%20I%20have%20shown%20the%20way%20to%20everyone.%20Instead%20of%20abusing%20me%2C%20why%20don't%20you%20implement%20it%20in%20your%2020%20states%2C%20then%20everyone%20will%20benefit%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20abuse%20me%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20National%20Convenor%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%2C%20will%20be%20launching%20the%20scheme%20from%20the%20Hanuman%20Temple%20at%20Connaught%20Place%2C%20while%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20will%20launch%20the%20scheme%20from%20the%20Gurudwara%20located%20in%20Karol%20Bagh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20along%20with%20my%20wife%2C%20I%20will%20launch%20the%20Priest%20Granthi%20Samman%20Yojana%20from%20the%20Hanuman%20Temple%20at%20Connaught%20Place.%20Atishi%20ji%20will%20launch%20this%20scheme%20from%20the%20Gurudwara%20located%20in%20Karol%20Bagh%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20announced%20the%20Pujari%20Granthi%20Samman%20Yojana%20which%20would%20be%20implemented%20once%20the%20AAP%20form%20the%20government%20winning%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20announcmenet%20of%20scheme%2C%20Delhi%20BJP%20President%20Virendraa%20Sachdeva%20on%20Monday%20attacked%20the%20AAP%20government%20after%20and%20said%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20now%20a%20defeated%20and%20desperate%20leader%20who%20is%20making%20%26quot%3Bpopulist%20announcements%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20the%20Delhi%20BJP%20chief%20said%20that%20the%20AAP%20knows%20they%20are%20going%20to%20lose%20Delhi%20elections%3B%20that's%20why%20they%20are%20remembering%20'Lord%20Ram.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20now%20a%20defeated%20and%20desperate%20leader%20who%20is%20making%20daily%20populist%20announcements%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%20They%20(Delhi%20government)%20have%20to%20reply%20in%20court%2C%20why%20they%20didn't%20pay%20for%20Priests%20and%20Granthis%20like%20Maulavis%20-%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20that%2C%20they%20have%20announced%20this%20scheme%20(Pujari%20Granthi%20Samman%20Yojana)...%20When%20you%20(AAP)%20see%20that%20you%20are%20losing%20ground%2C%20'tumhe%20Ram%20naam%20yaad%20aa%20raha%20hai'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sachdeva%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20pressure%20of%20the%20movement%20by%20the%20Delhi%20BJP%20and%20its%20Pujari%20Prakosht%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20forced%20to%20announce%20the%20Pujari%20Granthi%20Samman%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a