3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20can%20establish%20a%20nursery%20after%20their%20plants%20get%20two%20to%20three%20years%20old.%20This%20allows%20you%20to%20earn%20income%20from%20fruit%20sales%20for%20seven%20months%20and%20generate%20revenue%20throughout%20the%20year%20by%20selling%20saplings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20he%20earns%20Rs%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20annually%20from%20the%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20only%20sell%20fruits%2C%20you%20can%20earn%20up%20to%20four%20to%20five%20lakh%20rupees%20per%20acre%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnshul%20also%20points%20out%20that%20dragon%20fruit%20farming%20requires%20only%20a%20one-time%20investment%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20per%20acre.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20homemade%20%3Cem%3Ejeevamrit%20%3C%2Fem%3E(natural%20liquid%20fertiliser%20made%20from%20cow%20dung)%20to%20boost%20fruit%20size%20and%20soil%20fertility.%20Using%20natural%20fertilisers%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20your%20input%20costs%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnshul%E2%80%99s%20model%20showcases%20the%20potential%20for%20sustainable%20and%20profitable%20farming.%20He%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20risks%20in%20agriculture%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20historical%20figures%20like%20Vasco%20da%20Gama%20and%20Columbus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20had%20not%20ventured%20into%20the%20unknown%2C%20we%20may%20not%20have%20discovered%20the%20sea%20route%20to%20India%20and%20discovered%20America.%20My%20father%20also%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20fear%20taking%20risks%2C%20you%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20success%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%2C%20Anshul%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20quips%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20son%20has%20proved%20that%20if%20you%20are%20dedicated%20and%20consistent%20in%20your%20efforts%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20achieve%20success.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20fear%20taking%20risks%20and%20continue%20to%20toil%20in%20the%20field%20by%20growing%20crops%20that%20they%20are%20comfortable%20with%2C%20even%20though%20they%20are%20unprofitable.%20Remember%20that%20if%20you%20sell%20one%20sack%20(50%20kg)%20of%20wheat%2C%20you%20earn%20the%20same%20amount%20by%20selling%20just%20two%20kg%20of%20dragon%20fruits.%20So%2C%20you%20can%20reap%20substantial%20rewards%20now%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20changing%20climate%20that%20poses%20challenges%20to%20traditional%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Anshul%20Mishra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735529400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fdragon-fruits-1-1735304037.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D393426%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anshul%20Mishra%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20graduate%2C%20returned%20to%20his%20roots%20in%20Shahjahanpur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20to%20transform%20barren%20ancestral%20land%20into%20a%20thriving%20dragon%20fruit%20farm.%20Combining%20fresh%20fruit%20sales%20with%20a%20lucrative%20nursery%20business%2C%20he%20now%20generates%20impressive%20profits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A85%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F393426%2Fengineer-turned-farmer-grows-dragon-fruit-vertical-farming-earns-lakhs-nursery-business%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Investigators%20want%20to%20arrest%20South%20Korean%20president%20over%20martial%20law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735527360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F12%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-south-korea-yoon-suk-yeol_6773863.jpg%3F20241212065821