C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20posed%20a%20profound%20question%20for%20Shekhar%3A%20What%20future%20awaited%20the%20child%20without%20education%3F%20The%20realisation%20ignited%20a%20spark%20within%20him%2C%20inspiring%20him%20to%20dedicate%20his%20career%20to%20providing%20quality%20education%20for%20underprivileged%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1-1734543122.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20are%20rescued%20from%20factories%20in%20India%20and%20provided%20the%20life%20they%20deserve.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1-1734543122.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1-1734543122-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1-1734543122-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1-1734543122-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-1-1734543122-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390688%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildren%20are%20rescued%20from%20factories%20in%20India%20and%20given%20the%20life%20they%20deserve.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20idea%20was%20promising%2C%20Shekhar%20faced%20significant%20financial%20struggles%20to%20establish%20what%20he%20envisioned.%20%E2%80%9CCorporates%20did%20not%20come%20forward%20to%20provide%20funding%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20CSR%20mandate%20in