on%2C%20which%20can%20significantly%20impact%20healthcare%20costs.%20Moreover%2C%20pre-existing%20illnesses%20can%20influence%20health%20insurance%20premiums%2C%20potentially%20resulting%20in%20higher%20costs%20or%20even%20denial%20of%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20aims%20to%20change%20the%20lives%20of%20senior%20citizens%20in%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComprehensive%20Coverage%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cardholders%20can%20receive%20cashless%20treatment%20worth%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20annually%20at%20empanelled%20hospitals%20across%20India%2C%20covering%20an%20extensive%20range%20of%20medical%20procedures.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20find%20the%20extensive%20list%20of%20hospitals%20that%20come%20under%20the%20card%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnha.gov.in%2Fimg%2Fresources%2FPMJAY-Hospital-List.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInclusivity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Unlike%20schemes%20that%20target%20economically%20disadvantaged%20groups%2C%20this%20programme%20is%20universal%20for%20all%20citizens%20aged%2070%20and%20above%2C%20breaking%20socio-economic%20barriers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBeneficiaries%20can%20avail%20of%20treatments%20at%20any%20empanelled%20hospital%20nationwide%2C%20ensuring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333453%2Fkochi-startup-ansfrid-smartcare-emergency-alert-smart-watch-for-senior-citizens-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseamless%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20access%20even%20outside%20their%20home%20state.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Apply%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Health%20Authority%20(NHA)%20has%20simplified%20the%20registration%20process%20for%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Vaya%20Vandana%20card.%20Seniors%20can%20now%20register%20in%20multiple%20ways%3A%20online%20through%20the%20beneficiary%20portal%20(beneficiary.nha.gov.in)%20or%20the%20Ayushman%20app%2C%20or%20in%20person%20at%20PM-JAY%20empanelled%20hospitals%20and%20common%20service%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEligible%20individuals%20can%20complete%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20e-KYC%20through%20the%20National%20Health%20Authority%20website%20or%20Common%20Service%20Centres%20(CSCs)%20to%20register.%20After%20successful%20verification%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20receive%20the%20card%2C%20granting%20them%20access%20to%20cashless%20treatment%20at%20empanelled%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20commitment%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363871%2Fdr-ravinder-chowkidaar-sushruta-foundation-warangal-telangana-low-cost-free-surgery-healthcare-underprivileged%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20health%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20senior%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3A%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fwealth%2Finsure%2Fhealth-insurance%2Fwhat-is-ayushman-vaya-vandana-card-that-provides-free-hospital-treatment-for-all-senior-citizens-above-70-years%2Farticleshow%2F114766818.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20that%20provides%20free%20hospital%20treatment%20for%20all%20senior%20citizens%20above%2070%20years%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20The%20Economic%20Times%2C%20published%20on%202%20November%2C%202024%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finsurance%2Fstory%2Fayushman-bharat-vaya-vandana-full-state-wise-list-of-hospitals-entitled-to-serve-senior-citizens-for-ab-pm-jay-health-cover-452884-2024-11-07%5C%22%3EAyushman%20Bharat%20Vaya%20Vandana%3A%20Full%2C%20state-wise%20list%20of%20hospitals%20entitled%20to%20serve%20senior%20citizens%20for%20AB%20PM-JAY%20cover%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20Business%20Today%2C%20published%20on%207%20November%2C%202024%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnha.gov.in%2Fimg%2Fresources%2FPMJAY-Hospital-List.pdf%5C%22%3EPMJAY%20Hospital%20list%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20published%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735201800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D391125%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Revolutionising%20senior%20citizen%20healthcare%2C%20this%20card%20offers%20free%20medical%20treatment%20worth%20Rs%205%20lakh%20annually%20to%20those%20aged%2070%20and%20above%2C%20breaking%20financial%20barriers%20and%20ensuring%20dignity%20in%20care.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Mervin%20Preethi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391125%2Fayushman-vaya-vandana-card-senior-citizens-healthcare%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20Man%E2%80%99s%20Relentless%20Effort%20Helps%20400%20Nomads%20in%20Rajasthan%20Get%20the%20Documents%20Many%20Take%20for%20Granted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20Banjara%20tribe%20(a%20nomadic%20group%20that%20traditionally%20worked%20as%20traders%20of%20goods%20and%20cattle)%2C%20Paras%20grew%20up%20with%20the%20gnawing%20sense%20of%20an%20%E2%80%98us%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98them%E2%80%99%20divide.%20He%20saw%20the%20struggles%20faced%20by%20his%20people%20%E2%80%94%20discrimination%2C%20marginalisation%2C%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20basic%20rights%2C%20and%20most%20significantly%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20identity%20in%20a%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%2C%20like%20many%20others%20from%20the%20Banjara%20community%2C%20lived%20a%20life%20on%20the%20move%2C%20travelling%20and%20trading%20goods.%20His%20parents%20lived%20a%20nomadic%20existence%2C%20while%20Paras%E2%80%99s%20eight%20older%20siblings%20never%20even%20attended%20school%20due%20to%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20constant%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20and%20grandfather%20would%20sell%20salt%2C%20that%20used%20to%20be%20our%20trade.%20They%20also%20used%20to%20sell%20cattle%20to%20farmers%20who%20needed%20them%20for%20agriculture.%20At%20cattle%20fairs%20organised%20by%20the%20Government%2C%20they%20would%20buy%20and%20take%20the%20cattle%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20mainly%20to%20the%20southern%20regions.%20There%2C%20tribal%20farmers%20rely%20on%20cattle%20for%20farming%20instead%20of%20using%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20transportation%20methods%20improved%20and%20small%20markets%20began%20setting%20up%2C%20this%20line%20of%20business%20became%20obsolete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20then%20had%20to%20look%20for%20other%20ways%20of%20earning.%20With%20few%20options%20available%2C%20they%20shifted%20to%20labour%20work%20and%20formed%20a%20small%20community%20of%20labourers%20where%20everyone%20would%20work%20together.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20they%20decided%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20settle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paras%20Banjara%20addressing%20a%20Jan%20Sunwai%20to%20empower%20nomadic%20communities%20and%20help%20them%20raise%20their%20voices%20on%20important%20issues.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.38.35-AM-2-1734609378-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390971%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3